title: "SURGE: Surrogate Regression Engine"
message: "If you use SURGE in your research, please cite this software."
type: software
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-04-21"
license: BSD-3-Clause
url: "https://github.com/asvillar/SURGE"
repository-code: "https://github.com/asvillar/SURGE"
keywords:
  - surrogate-models
