  - pytorch
  - scikit-learn
  - onnx
abstract: >-
  SURGE is a Python framework for building, training, evaluating, and deploying
  scientific surrogate regression models. It provides a unified engine for
  scikit-learn, PyTorch, and GPflow backends; a declarative workflow spec;
  lightweight hyperparameter optimization via Optuna; ONNX export for
  inference; and a per-run provenance bundle (resources_used, model profile,
  scalers, model card) aimed at reproducibility in HPC environments.
